"This option displays a copy of <quote>The &kaddressbook; Handbook</quote> "
"via the &khelpcenter; utility program."
msgstr ""
"Alternativet visar en kopia av <quote>Handbok Addressbok</quote> via "
"programverktyget Hjälpcentral."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
